name: 16th International Conference on Orthopedics, Osteoporosis & Trauma
content: Orthopedics 2022 takes immense pleasure in welcoming all the participants from across the globe to attend “16th International Conference on Orthopedics, Osteoporosis & Trauma” during September 19-20, 2022 at London, UK. The conference comprises eminent personalities with their keynote presentations, verbal speeches, productive poster presentations, workshop, and exhibitions along with a discussion forum providing the insights on the Orthopedics.
